data.description: Welcome to this diamond in the rough located in the desirable Greater Dellcrest neighborhood of San Antonio! This charming home's 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, large living space and converted garage provides the perfect space for comfortable family living. While some minor repairs and updates may be desired, the possibilities are endless to customize and really make this gem your own.  The fenced yard is large and has a patio right off the dining/kitchen area that's perfect for sitting and relaxing or entertaining and barbequing.  Schedule a showing today or visit our upcoming open house on February 3, 12-3pm.
